{
  "stem": "7017.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I got a job and not far away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From five miles of Sosnowiec is Katowice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Katowice used to belong once, before the First World War, to Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Still with my family, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was a sick man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't care what happened, so he didn't work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brothers worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We took every day to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Katowice was a big museum, a new museum.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took it apart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They broke  it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every stone, they took out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It took years just to do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a foreman, a Jewish foreman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we have to be there every morning and go and come back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this was not forced labor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If not-- my youngest brother, 1939, or beginning of '40, they took him right away to the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, we have five brothers, one's got to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See, it was a Jewish-- and the police, they said, if one goes to the concentration camp, the rest will be safe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it went on and on-- and later, the second one-- was just to hold the people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was the youngest, so he wants to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was 17 years old, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Germany.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He later went to the concentration camp, when the Judenlager, he went to the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was five years.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He lives in Israel right now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He did survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the beginning, I also sent packages to the camp with food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it was hard to send money sometimes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was smart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He told me to take a piece of soap-- soap that you wash your hand with-- you make a hole and put some money inside, paper money, and lay the cover back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a factory, just a place.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
